  "html_size": 199889,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110166346775\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110166346775\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028548_9'\">\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">[가정의달 이벤트/어버이날 선물/스승의날 선물]</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">어버이날 선물, 스승의날</span><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">&nbsp;선물은 경옥고, 공진단으로 추천합니다</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">5월은 가정의 달인 만큼&nbsp; 선물 고민을 많이 하시죠?</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">건강을 위한 선물은 어떠신가요?</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">이수한의원에서는 가정의달을 맞이하여 공진단/경옥고를 15% 할인 이벤트를 합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/68a328f4d7bf6428.png\" width=\"394\" height=\"95\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 394px; rheight: 95px\" id=\"20130416_215/isuhani_1366115076160JPVRt_PNG/%B0%A8%BB%E7%C0%CC%BA%A5%C6%AE1.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66D0C17')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/68a328f4d7bf6428.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">공진단은 황실에서 최고의 보약으로&nbsp; 복용한 만큼 그 약효를 인정받아온 명약 입니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">특별히 몸이 아프지 않아도&nbsp; 누구나 복용하기 좋아서 어버이날이나 스승의날 건강선물로 추천합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/246f2ee95ab68a82.jpg\" width=\"404\" height=\"404\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 404px; rheight: 404px\" id=\"20130416_89/isuhani_13661162306534eELY_JPEG/%B0%F8%C1%F8%B4%DC%C7%D5%C4%A1%B1%E2%BB%E7%C1%F8.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66D0C17')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/246f2ee95ab68a82.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #c2c2c2; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">어버이날 선물/스승의날 선물 추천</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><strong><font color=\"#d1b274\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;공진단의 주요성분&gt;</font></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4db740d05650f1af.png\" width=\"530\" height=\"197\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 530px; rheight: 197px\" id=\"20130416_298/isuhani_1366118062964wenyy_PNG/%B0%F8%C1%F8%B4%DC%BC%BA%BA%D0.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66D0C17')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4db740d05650f1af.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;공진단의 효능&gt;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">잦은 음주, 스트레스로 인해 간기능이 떨어진 사람</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;성장 발육 부진으로 키가 잘 안크는 어린이</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 출산 후 냉혈과 기력소모가 심한 여성</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 허약체질, 양기부족, 만성피로, 원기회복, 노화방지, 치매예방</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">경옥고는 소화에 부담이 없고 누구나 복용할 수 있는 약입니다</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">정력이 부족한 것을 보충하여 골수를 돕고 근골을 튼튼하게 하여 병을 예방한다고 알려져 있습니다</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/226e5bd969ad87fd.jpg\" width=\"404\" height=\"404\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 404px; rheight: 404px\" id=\"20130416_77/isuhani_1366119200979TgkBu_JPEG/%B0%E6%BF%C1%B0%ED%C7%D5%C4%A1%B1%E2%BB%E7%C1%F8.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66D0C17')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/226e5bd969ad87fd.jpg\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 9pt; COLOR: #c2c2c2; FONT-FAMILY: '7367_9'\">어버이날 선물/스승의날 선물 추천</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">동의 보감에서 오래 살게 하고 건강하게 하는 약 중에서 </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">가장 먼저 기재되어 있을 정도로 정성이 깃든 귀한 보약입니다</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #cfcca2\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #cfcca2\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;</span><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">경옥고의 주요</span></span><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">성분&gt;</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8487c9d23224818e.png\" width=\"523\" height=\"199\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 523px; rheight: 199px\" id=\"20130416_207/isuhani_1366119884500sY055_PNG/%B0%E6%BF%C1%B0%ED%BC%BA%BA%D0.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66D0C17')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8487c9d23224818e.png\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;경옥고의 효능&gt;</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">갱년기 장애 개선, 수험생 건강회복, 만성피로, 허약체질개선</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 성장촉진, 집중력 강화, 마른기침 및 호흡기 질환, 변비개선</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130417_275/isuhani_13661584729733toKy_JPEG/%C6%F7%BD%BA%C6%AE%C0%CF.PNG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"160\" height=\"148\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 160px; rheight: 148px\" id=\"20130417_275/isuhani_13661584729733toKy_JPEG/%C6%F7%BD%BA%C6%AE%C0%CF.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A66D0C17')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130417_275/isuhani_13661584729733toKy_JPEG/%C6%F7%BD%BA%C6%AE%C0%CF.PNG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"></span></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #000000\"><strong>가정의달 이벤트 신청기간 : 4월22일 ~ 5월3일까지<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #ff0000\"> </span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #000000\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: #ff0000\">&nbsp;(신청기간에 주문해주시는 분들에 한해 할인혜택)</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"COLOR: #d1b274\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000000\"><span style=\"COLOR: #000